title: The Grove Veggie Kitchen
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Salad bar, Take-out, European, Irish
description: Small, centrally located vegetarian deli restaurant established by a mother and daughter team since 1981. Gets a busy lunchtime crowd (best to go at noon). In the display case you will find dishes like quiche, salad, and curry, and stew. Vegans should ask what's suitable.
